|-
| ABORT || $0000 || Abort (unused)
|-
| NMI || $8342 || Non-maskable interrupt (VBlank)
|-
| RESET || $0000 || Reset (native, unused)
|-
| IRQ || $85A5 || Hardware interrupt
|}

